Paper: hep-th/0304092

Date: 2003-04-09

Title: Bethe Ansatz solution of the open XXZ chain with nondiagonal boundary

termsAuthors: Rafael I. Nepomechie

Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX; amssymb, amsmath, no figures; v2

We propose a set of conventional Bethe Ansatz equations and a correspondingexpression for the eigenvalues of the transfer matrix for the open spin-1/2 XXZquantum spin chain with nondiagonal boundary terms, provided that the boundaryparameters obey a certain linear relation.